mixin HeroHeader
  section.pt-7
    .container
      .row.align-items-center

        .col-md-6.text-md-start.text-center.py-6

          h1.mb-4.fs-9.fw-bold The Design Thinking Superpowers
          p.mb-6.lead.text-secondary Tools tutorials, design and innovation experts, all
            br.d-none.d-xl-block
            | in one place! The most intuitive way to imagine
            br.d-none.d-xl-block
            | your next user experience.
          .text-center.text-md-start
            a.btn.btn-warning.me-3.btn-lg(href='#!' role='button') Get started
            a.btn.btn-link.text-warning.fw-medium(href='#!' role='button' data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#popupVideo")
              span.fas.fa-play.me-2
              | Watch the video    

        .col-md-6.text-end
          img.pt-7.pt-md-0.img-fluid(src=`${CWD}assets/img/hero/hero-img.png` alt='')